---
const products = [
  {
    image: '/images/logo-mlieko.png',
    title: 'Kozie mlieko',
    tag: 'Nepasterizované',
    description: 'Čerstvé kozie mlieko od našich kôz chovaných pôvodným spôsobom. Bez pasterizácie, tak ako má byť.',
  },
  {
    image: '/images/logo-syr.png',
    title: 'Kozí syr',
    tag: 'Z nepasterizovaného mlieka',
    description: 'Poctivý kozí syr vyrobený z nášho mlieka. Jemná chuť, žiadne zbytočné prísady.',
  },
];
---

<section id="produkty" class="py-20 md:py-24 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="eyebrow text-wine text-xs mb-3">Z kozej farmy</p>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-ink mb-5">Produkty z kozieho mlieka</h2>
      <div class="stamp-divider text-wheat-dark mb-6">
        <span class="rule"></span><span class="dot"></span><span class="rule"></span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-ink-soft max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Domáce produkty od našich kôz. Predávame ich priamo na farme — bez sprostredkovateľov.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      {products.map((p) => (
        <div class="bg-cream-card rounded-lg border border-ink/15 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 p-8 text-center flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="w-44 h-44 mb-6">
            <img src={p.image} alt={`${p.title} – FARMA KORAGOLD-ABM`} class="w-full h-full object-contain drop-shadow-md" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <span class="inline-block eyebrow text-[10px] text-sage-dark bg-sage/15 border border-sage/30 rounded-full px-3 py-1 mb-3">{p.tag}</span>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-ink mb-3">{p.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">{p.description}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- No e-shop notice -->
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-12 text-center bg-sage/10 border border-sage/25 rounded-lg px-6 py-5">
      <p class="text-ink-soft mb-4">
        <strong class="text-ink">Predaj len priamo na farme.</strong> Nemáme e-shop ani online objednávky —
        o dostupnosti a cene sa informujte telefonicky.
      </p>
      <a href="tel:+421950466433"
         class="btn-vintage bg-sage hover:bg-sage-dark text-cream py-3 px-7 text-sm">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
        </svg>
        Zavolať · 0950 466 433
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
